    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is a concours-grade E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine. This naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS to achieve an 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and an M Variable Differential Lock, the drivetrain provides an unfiltered, analog connection to the road. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), maintaining perfect suspension kinematics. This example is in pristine aesthetic condition with original factory paint and a flawless interior. Critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, has been documented to ensure mechanical longevity. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
