      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in showroom condition. The exterior features the original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like gloss, protected by a professional ceramic coating. There are absolutely no dings, chips, or scratches to be found. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or cracking. Every electronic feature, from the immersive surround-sound system to the advanced navigation suite, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, this car has been pampered with a meticulous maintenance schedule at authorized service centers, and it has been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. With exceptionally low mileage and a clean history, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that feels and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
