    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically flawless example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 engineering. The 3.2L inline-six features a fully overhauled dual-VANOS system and documented rod bearing replacement, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline is explored with total confidence. Power is transferred via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally optimized with a comprehensive subframe reinforcement kit and refreshed suspension geometry featuring Koni Yellow dampers for superior damping ratios. This specimen retains its factory-correct kinematic profile and exhibits zero oxidative stress or fluid seepage. An investment-grade driver\u2019s car for the technical purist.",
